structure.unit: DIVISION OF INSURANCE AND INSURANCE GENERALLY (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 2. -- Repealed and reenacted 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 106, sec. 4, effective June 17, 1948. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 100, sec. 4, effective October 1, 1947.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Filing of rate manuals and plans; supporting information; filing through rating organization; review of filings; waiting periods; when filings effective; special filings; permission for excess rate; policies must conform to filed rates.
